data.title: Star Gazing: Nia Long Celebrates 40th Birthday in NYC | Essence
data.meta_description: A glowing Nia Long celebrates her birthday party sponsored by Belvedere and catered by "Top Chef Masters" winner Marcus Samuelsson in New York City. The beloved actress will turn the big 4-0 on October 30. She looks stunning!
